lines.text: Do you think I'm going to let that little gangster do this and get away with it?
Then you'll be takin' the 9 o'clock walk. You'll be topped for certain.
An I'll tell you something else. You bring Bob Stevens here and I'll kill 'im, see? Then you really will have something to worry about.
How would you describe the men who attacked you?
As dirty lot of stinking rotten sons of...
Alright, alright. What did they look like?
'Ow the hell should I know? D'you suppose they came up and raised their bloomin' 'ats before they 'it me?
